# Template for /root/.config/vault-to-ssm/.env on the Hostinger VPS.
#
# Copy → fill → `chmod 0600` + `chown root:root`. NEVER commit a filled-in copy.
#
# Loaded by /usr/local/sbin/vault-to-ssm-sync. Required by the systemd unit
# /etc/systemd/system/vault-to-ssm-sync.service.
#
# Tracks: AFF-245 M4. Plan: docs/plans/SECRETS-MIGRATION.md § M4.

# ---- Vault endpoint + sync token ---------------------------------------
#
# VAULT_TOKEN should be a SCOPED token (NOT the initial root). Create it
# after M3 lands by running on operator laptop:
#
#     vault policy write sync-to-ssm - <<'EOF'
#     path "platform/data/staging/*"    { capabilities = ["read"] }
#     path "platform/data/production/*" { capabilities = ["read"] }
#     EOF
#     vault token create -policy=sync-to-ssm -ttl=8760h -display-name=ssm-sync \
#       -renewable=true
#
# Paste the resulting `hvs.XXX` token here. Rotate 90-day.
VAULT_ADDR=https://secrets-admin.afframe.com
VAULT_TOKEN=<paste-scoped-vault-token-after-M3>

# ---- AWS credentials for ssm:PutParameter ------------------------------
#
# This is a separate IAM user (NOT vault-unseal-vps, NOT vault-aws-auth-verifier)
# whose permissions are scoped to:
#   ssm:PutParameter, ssm:GetParameter on /monorepo/*/{better-auth-secret,resend-api-key,sync-heartbeat}
#   kms:GenerateDataKey on the default aws/ssm key
#
# Will be provisioned by SecretsBootstrap CDK stack in PR-D (the CDK
# refactor that lands `vault-ssm-sync` IAM user + the migrated secret
# references). Until then, the simplest interim path is to attach a
# minimal inline policy to the existing operator user with:
#   - ssm:PutParameter, ssm:GetParameter on
#     /monorepo/{staging,production}/{better-auth-secret,resend-api-key,sync-heartbeat}
#   - kms:GenerateDataKey, kms:Decrypt on alias/aws/ssm
#
# Access keys (interim or post-PR-D) generated via:
#
#     aws iam create-access-key --user-name vault-ssm-sync
#
# Store both fields in macOS Keychain:
#   afframe-vault-ssm-sync-access-key-id
#   afframe-vault-ssm-sync-secret-access-key
#
# Rotate 90-day.
AWS_REGION=eu-central-1
AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=<paste-vault-ssm-sync-access-key-id>
AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=<paste-vault-ssm-sync-secret-access-key>
